   "source": [
    "def impute_age(cols):\n",
    "    Age = cols[0]\n",
    "    Pclass = cols[1]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if pd.isnull(Age):\n",
    "        if Pclass == 1:\n",
    "            return(38)\n",
    "        elif Pclass == 2:\n",
    "            return(29)\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            return(24)\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        return(Age)"
   ]
  },

   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "train['Age'] = train[['Age','Pclass']].apply(impute_age,axis=1) #axis = 1 along columns"
